comments: Mudiay (NYK) trips Caruso (LAL) and affects his SQBR.
Jordan (NYK) briefly grasps Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) arm off ball and does not affect his ability to defend the pass in the post.
Jordan (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Caruso (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Kuzma (LAL) gives Dotson (NYK) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
James (LAL) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
James (LAL) makes slight contact with Hezonja (NYK) during the drive but he does not extend his forearm to dislodge him.
Hezonja (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position on Williams (LAL) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Williams (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Mudiay (NYK) at the end of the drive by jumping vertically to absorb the contact.
Jordan (NYK) is imminently attempting a shot within three seconds.
Kuzma (LAL) makes contact to Jordan's (NYK) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Hezonja (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position on James (LAL) during the drive.
Multiple video angles show that Jordan (NYK) appears to block the shot just prior to it making contact with the backboard.
Hezonja (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by James (LAL).
Williams (LAL) does not impede Jordan (NYK) when he grabs the rebound and tries to shoot.
Caruso (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Mudiay (NYK) in transition.
Hezonja (NYK) makes marginal contact with James (LAL) that does not affect his SQBR.
Williams (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hezonja (NYK) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Williams (LAL) and Jordan (NYK) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) moves laterally into the path of Mudiay (NYK) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.

Hezonja (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by James (LAL).  He makes clean contact with the ball when he first reaches in and then cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
